    {"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Cultural Context"}],"depth":2,"type":"heading"},
    {"children":[{"type":"text","value":"划船 is both a practical transportation method and recreational activity in Chinese culture. Dragon\nboat racing (赛龙舟) is a traditional festival activity that uses the concept of 划船. In parks and\nscenic areas, 划船 is a popular leisure activity for families and couples, often seen as romantic\nand peaceful, connecting people with nature and water."}],"type":"paragraph"}
